---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Arky Foundation - Neutral Accountability Standard"
  description="Arky is a neutral public standard for accountable action across agents, money, chains, and machines. Signed, content-addressed receipts any system can replay."
  canonicalPath="/"
>
  <main id="main">
    <section class="hero" id="top" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
      <div class="hero-top">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <p class="kicker reveal hero-load">Neutral accountability layer&ensp;·&ensp;ARKY-TIM-v1</p>
          <h1 id="hero-title" class="reveal hero-load" style="--reveal-delay: 60ms"><span class="h1-mark">Arky</span></h1>
          <p class="tagline reveal hero-load" style="--reveal-delay: 120ms">A public standard for action and verification across agents, money, chains, and machines.</p>
          <p class="subline reveal hero-load" style="--reveal-delay: 180ms">Every action records who acted, on what evidence, under which policy, and what happened &mdash; as a signed, content-addressed receipt any system can replay.</p>
          <div class="hero-actions reveal hero-load" style="--reveal-delay: 240ms" aria-label="Primary actions">
            <a class="button primary" href="https://github.com/arky-foundation/arky.foundation/blob/master/specs/core/ARKY-TIM-v1.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Read the spec</a>
            <a class="button" href="https://github.com/arky-foundation/arky.foundation/blob/master/CONFORMANCE.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Run vectors</a>
            <a class="button" href="https://github.com/arky-foundation/arky.foundation/blob/master/packages/core/README.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Implement</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-net reveal hero-load" style="--reveal-delay: 340ms">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 400 400" role="img" aria-labelledby="net-title net-desc">
            <title id="net-title">Arky actor network</title>
            <desc id="net-desc">AI agents, space devices, banks, and blockchains exchange signed evidence and receipts through a neutral Arky hub at the center.</desc>

            <!-- engineering grid + orbit rings -->
            <g class="net-grid">
              <path d="M40 200H360M200 40V360"></path>
              <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="158"></circle>
            </g>
            <circle class="net-orbit spin" cx="200" cy="200" r="118"></circle>
            <circle class="net-orbit" cx="200" cy="200" r="158"></circle>

            <!-- static spokes (actor -> hub), then live animated overlays -->
            <g class="net-spoke">
              <path d="M200 200L96 96"></path>
              <path d="M200 200L304 96"></path>
              <path d="M200 200L304 304"></path>
              <path d="M200 200L96 304"></path>
            </g>
            <g aria-hidden="true">
              <path class="net-spoke-live inbound" d="M96 96L200 200" style="animation-delay:0s"></path>
              <path class="net-spoke-live outbound" d="M200 200L304 96" style="animation-delay:-0.9s"></path>
              <path class="net-spoke-live inbound" d="M304 304L200 200" style="animation-delay:-1.8s"></path>
              <path class="net-spoke-live outbound" d="M200 200L96 304" style="animation-delay:-2.7s"></path>
            </g>

            <!-- ACTOR: AI agent (top-left) — robot head -->
            <g class="net-node" data-actor="agent" transform="translate(96 96)" aria-label="AI agent">
              <rect class="net-chip" x="-30" y="-30" width="60" height="60" rx="9"></rect>
              <!-- Lucide "bot" -->
              <g class="net-glyph" transform="translate(-18 -18) scale(1.5)">
                <path d="M12 8V4H8"></path>
                <rect width="16" height="12" x="4" y="8" rx="2"></rect>
                <path d="M2 14h2"></path>
                <path d="M20 14h2"></path>
                <path d="M15 13v2"></path>
                <path d="M9 13v2"></path>
              </g>
              <text class="net-name" x="0" y="44" text-anchor="middle">Agents</text>
            </g>

            <!-- ACTOR: Space device (top-right) -->
            <g class="net-node" data-actor="space" transform="translate(304 96)" aria-label="Space device">
              <rect class="net-chip" x="-30" y="-30" width="60" height="60" rx="9"></rect>
              <!-- Lucide "satellite" -->
              <g class="net-glyph" transform="translate(-18 -18) scale(1.5)">
                <path d="m13.5 6.5-3.148-3.148a1.205 1.205 0 0 0-1.704 0L6.352 5.648a1.205 1.205 0 0 0 0 1.704L9.5 10.5"></path>
                <path d="M16.5 7.5 19 5"></path>
                <path d="m17.5 10.5 3.148 3.148a1.205 1.205 0 0 1 0 1.704l-2.296 2.296a1.205 1.205 0 0 1-1.704 0L13.5 14.5"></path>
                <path d="M9 21a6 6 0 0 0-6-6"></path>
                <path d="M9.352 10.648a1.205 1.205 0 0 0 0 1.704l2.296 2.296a1.205 1.205 0 0 0 1.704 0l4.296-4.296a1.205 1.205 0 0 0 0-1.704l-2.296-2.296a1.205 1.205 0 0 0-1.704 0z"></path>
              </g>
              <text class="net-name" x="0" y="44" text-anchor="middle">Space</text>
            </g>

            <!-- ACTOR: Bank (bottom-right) -->
            <g class="net-node" data-actor="bank" transform="translate(304 304)" aria-label="Bank">
              <rect class="net-chip" x="-30" y="-30" width="60" height="60" rx="9"></rect>
              <!-- Lucide "landmark" -->
              <g class="net-glyph" transform="translate(-18 -18) scale(1.5)">
                <path d="M10 18v-7"></path>
                <path d="M11.119 2.205a2 2 0 0 1 1.762 0l7.84 3.846A.5.5 0 0 1 20.5 7h-17a.5.5 0 0 1-.22-.949z"></path>
                <path d="M14 18v-7"></path>
                <path d="M18 18v-7"></path>
                <path d="M3 22h18"></path>
                <path d="M6 18v-7"></path>
              </g>
              <text class="net-name" x="0" y="44" text-anchor="middle">Banks</text>
            </g>

            <!-- ACTOR: Blockchain (bottom-left) -->
            <g class="net-node" data-actor="chain" transform="translate(96 304)" aria-label="Blockchain">
              <rect class="net-chip" x="-30" y="-30" width="60" height="60" rx="9"></rect>
              <!-- Lucide "link" -->
              <g class="net-glyph" transform="translate(-18 -18) scale(1.5)">
                <path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"></path>
                <path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"></path>
              </g>
              <text class="net-name" x="0" y="44" text-anchor="middle">Chains</text>
            </g>

            <!-- CENTRAL ARKY HUB -->
            <g aria-hidden="true">
              <circle class="net-hub-pulse" cx="200" cy="200" r="32"></circle>
              <circle class="net-hub-ring" cx="200" cy="200" r="32"></circle>
              <path class="net-hub-mark" d="M184 200h7l4-10 6 20 4-10h7"></path>
              <text class="net-hub-label" x="200" y="252">ARKY</text>
            </g>

            <!-- travelling packets, positioned by script -->
            <circle class="net-packet evidence" id="net-packet-a" cx="96" cy="96" r="3.4"></circle>
            <circle class="net-packet" id="net-packet-b" cx="200" cy="200" r="3.4"></circle>
          </svg>
          <span class="net-readout" aria-hidden="true">evidence in <b>&middot;</b> signed receipt out</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-stage reveal hero-load" style="--reveal-delay: 380ms" aria-label="Arky protocol schematic">
        <svg class="stage-svg" viewBox="0 0 1440 440" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" role="img" aria-labelledby="schematic-title schematic-desc">
          <title id="schematic-title">Arky protocol flow</title>
          <desc id="schematic-desc">Evidence moves through witness, decision, execution, and receipt stages, ending in a signed receipt.</desc>
          <defs>
            <marker id="arrow" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="8" refY="5" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" orient="auto-start-reverse">
              <path d="M0 0L10 5L0 10Z" fill="var(--lines)"></path>
            </marker>
          </defs>

          <!-- Faint circuit substrate spanning the stage -->
          <g class="schematic-faint">
            <path d="M40 70h180l30-30h160l30 30h300M900 70h120l40-40h160l40 40h120"></path>
            <path d="M40 372h220l34 34h220M740 406h160l40-34h260l40 34h160"></path>
            <path d="M120 96v-46M520 100v-50M1000 96v-46M1320 100v-50"></path>
            <path d="M40 200h60M40 240h44M1340 200h60M1356 240h44"></path>
          </g>
          <g class="schematic-oxide">
            <path d="M40 300h260l40-40h220l40 40h300"></path>
            <path d="M1040 300h120l40-40h200"></path>
          </g>

          <!-- Main signal route across the full width -->
          <path class="schematic-line" d="M150 220C300 100 430 100 580 220S830 340 980 220S1230 100 1300 220" marker-end="url(#arrow)"></path>
          <path class="live-route" id="live-route" d="M150 220C300 100 430 100 580 220S830 340 980 220S1230 100 1300 220"></path>

          <!-- Dimension ticks at route endpoints -->
          <g class="schematic-faint">
            <path d="M150 244v-12M150 220h-12M1300 244v-12M1300 220h12"></path>
          </g>

          <!-- Via dots along the substrate -->
          <g class="bp-via" opacity="0.5">
            <circle cx="250" cy="40" r="2.4"></circle><circle cx="440" cy="40" r="2.4"></circle>
            <circle cx="1020" cy="30" r="2.4"></circle><circle cx="1220" cy="30" r="2.4"></circle>
            <circle cx="294" cy="406" r="2.4"></circle><circle cx="514" cy="406" r="2.4"></circle>
            <circle cx="900" cy="406" r="2.4"></circle>
          </g>

          <g class="flow-node" data-step="0" data-active="true" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-label="Stage 1: TIM, evidence">
            <rect class="node-box" x="70" y="178" width="170" height="92" rx="5"></rect>
            <line class="node-pin" x1="70" y1="200" x2="54" y2="200"></line>
            <line class="node-pin" x1="70" y1="248" x2="54" y2="248"></line>
            <text class="node-label" x="96" y="220">TIM</text>
            <text class="node-role" x="96" y="244">Evidence</text>
          </g>

          <g class="flow-node" data-step="1" data-active="false" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-label="Stage 2: Notary, witness">
            <rect class="node-box" x="478" y="60" width="186" height="92" rx="5"></rect>
            <line class="node-pin" x1="571" y1="152" x2="571" y2="170"></line>
            <text class="node-label" x="504" y="102">Notary</text>
            <text class="node-role" x="504" y="126">Witness</text>
          </g>

          <g class="flow-node" data-step="2" data-active="false" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-label="Stage 3: Kernel, policy">
            <rect class="node-box" x="632" y="288" width="176" height="92" rx="5"></rect>
            <line class="node-pin" x1="720" y1="288" x2="720" y2="270"></line>
            <text class="node-label" x="658" y="330">Kernel</text>
            <text class="node-role" x="658" y="354">Policy</text>
          </g>

          <g class="flow-node" data-step="3" data-active="false" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-label="Stage 4: Settler, execute">
            <rect class="node-box" x="876" y="60" width="186" height="92" rx="5"></rect>
            <line class="node-pin" x1="969" y1="152" x2="969" y2="170"></line>
            <text class="node-label" x="902" y="102">Settler</text>
            <text class="node-role" x="902" y="126">Execute</text>
          </g>

          <g class="flow-node" data-step="4" data-active="false" tabindex="0" role="button" aria-label="Stage 5: XR, receipt">
            <rect class="node-box" x="1200" y="178" width="170" height="92" rx="5"></rect>
            <line class="node-pin" x1="1370" y1="200" x2="1386" y2="200"></line>
            <line class="node-pin" x1="1370" y1="248" x2="1386" y2="248"></line>
            <text class="node-label" x="1226" y="220">XR</text>
            <text class="node-role" x="1226" y="244">Receipt</text>
          </g>

          <circle class="signal-halo" id="signal-halo" cx="150" cy="220" r="11"></circle>
          <circle class="signal-dot" id="signal-dot" cx="150" cy="220" r="6"></circle>
        </svg>
        <div class="stage-edge-fade" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="stage-controls reveal hero-load" style="--reveal-delay: 440ms">
        <div class="stage-meta">
          <span class="readout">
            <span>signal <strong id="active-stage">TIM / Evidence</strong></span>
            <span class="receipt">signed receipt path</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <div class="depth-toggle" role="group" aria-label="Explanation depth">
          <button type="button" class="depth-btn" data-mode="plain" aria-pressed="true">Plain</button>
          <button type="button" class="depth-btn" data-mode="engineer" aria-pressed="false">Engineer</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="stage-desc" id="stage-desc" aria-live="polite"></p>
    </section>

    <section class="band section" id="standard" aria-labelledby="standard-title">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="section-grid">
          <div class="section-head reveal">
            <p class="section-label">What Arky is</p>
            <h2 id="standard-title">A public protocol for accountable action.</h2>
            <p class="head-note">A minimal record of who acted, on what evidence, under which policy, and what actually happened.</p>
          </div>
          <p class="lead reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 100ms">Five artifacts form one chain. Each is a signed, content-addressed document that references the one before it &mdash; so the whole sequence, from raw evidence to final receipt, can be replayed and verified independently. The right column is the exact algorithm each step is pinned to.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="dim" aria-hidden="true"><span class="dim-label">CORE ARTIFACTS&ensp;·&ensp;TIM &rarr; NOTARY &rarr; KERNEL &rarr; SETTLER &rarr; XR</span></div>
        <div class="spec-register reveal" aria-label="Core artifact register">
          <div class="spec-row">
            <span class="spec-idx">01</span>
            <span class="spec-name"><b>TIM</b><span>Evidence</span></span>
            <span class="spec-desc">Signed, content-addressed evidence: who, what, when.</span>
            <span class="spec-algo">cid = <b>multibase</b>(<b>multihash</b>(<span class="ox">sha2-256</span>, JCS(body)))</span>
          </div>
          <div class="spec-row">
            <span class="spec-idx">02</span>
            <span class="spec-name"><b>Notary</b><span>Witness</span></span>
            <span class="spec-desc">Fixes time, order, and finality; optional chain or log anchor.</span>
            <span class="spec-algo"><span class="ox">merkle-sha256-v1</span> root &middot; inclusion proof</span>
          </div>
          <div class="spec-row">
            <span class="spec-idx">03</span>
            <span class="spec-name"><b>Kernel</b><span>Policy</span></span>
            <span class="spec-desc">Deterministic decision under declared policy packs.</span>
            <span class="spec-algo">eval(assertions, <span class="ox">policy</span>) &rarr; allow / deny</span>
          </div>
          <div class="spec-row">
            <span class="spec-idx">04</span>
            <span class="spec-name"><b>Settler</b><span>Execute</span></span>
            <span class="spec-desc">Runs a verb on a rail: bank, chain, or device.</span>
            <span class="spec-algo">verb(<span class="ox">idempotency-key</span>) on rail</span>
          </div>
          <div class="spec-row">
            <span class="spec-idx">05</span>
            <span class="spec-name"><b>XR</b><span>Receipt</span></span>
            <span class="spec-desc">Signed outcome tied to the decision, rail, and anchors.</span>
            <span class="spec-algo">JWS <span class="ox">Ed25519</span> &middot; RFC 7797 b64:false</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="band section" id="conformance" aria-labelledby="conformance-title">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="section-grid">
          <div class="section-head reveal">
            <p class="section-label">Conformance</p>
            <h2 id="conformance-title">Vectors over vibes.</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="lead reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 100ms">Conformance is pass/fail, not marketing. The verifier recomputes content IDs, signatures, witnesses, Merkle roots, finality, and Settler transitions from inputs &mdash; then compares to each vector's expected output.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="metric-row reveal" aria-label="Conformance metrics">
          <div class="metric">
            <span class="num">100<em>/</em>100</span>
            <span class="cap">published vectors passing<br>on the reference stack</span>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <span class="num">2</span>
            <span class="cap">independent implementations<br>TypeScript &middot; Rust, cross-checked byte-for-byte</span>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <span class="num">L2</span>
            <span class="cap">core-loop coverage<br>production-ready manifests</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="dim" aria-hidden="true"><span class="dim-label">SUITE LEVELS&ensp;·&ensp;A SPEC IS STABLE ONLY WHEN ≥2 IMPLEMENTATIONS PASS</span></div>
        <div class="ledger reveal" aria-label="Conformance levels by suite">
          <div class="ledger-head" aria-hidden="true">
            <span>Suite</span><span>Levels</span><span style="text-align:right">Vectors</span><span style="justify-self:end">Status</span>
          </div>
          <div class="ledger-row">
            <span class="ledger-suite">TIM</span>
            <span class="ledger-levels">C1 canonicalize &middot; C2 hash+sign &middot; C3 cross-verify &middot; T1 verify</span>
            <span class="ledger-count">7+</span>
            <span class="pass-pill">Pass</span>
          </div>
          <div class="ledger-row">
            <span class="ledger-suite">Notary</span>
            <span class="ledger-levels">N1 witness &middot; N2 anchor (Merkle/inclusion) &middot; N3 finality depth</span>
            <span class="ledger-count">N1–N3</span>
            <span class="pass-pill">Pass</span>
          </div>
          <div class="ledger-row">
            <span class="ledger-suite">Kernel</span>
            <span class="ledger-levels">K1 eval &middot; K2 policy-aware &middot; K3 orchestrated</span>
            <span class="ledger-count">K1</span>
            <span class="pass-pill">Pass</span>
          </div>
          <div class="ledger-row">
            <span class="ledger-suite">Settlers</span>
            <span class="ledger-levels">S1 basic &middot; S2 idempotency/cascade &middot; S3 compensation/transitions</span>
            <span class="ledger-count">S1–S3</span>
            <span class="pass-pill">Pass</span>
          </div>
          <div class="ledger-row">
            <span class="ledger-suite">Ratification</span>
            <span class="ledger-levels">formal TC vote to Stable &middot; vectors + cross-check already hold</span>
            <span class="ledger-count">&mdash;</span>
            <span class="pass-pill pending">Pending</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="band section" id="adopt" aria-labelledby="adopt-title">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="section-grid">
          <div class="section-head reveal">
            <p class="section-label">Adoption path</p>
            <h2 id="adopt-title">Read. Verify. Ship.</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="lead reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 100ms">Technical adoption, not a signup. Validate artifacts locally, compare behavior against the vectors, then implement the loop in your stack against two executable reference anchors.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="path-grid">
          <article class="path-card reveal">
            <p class="claim">1 / SPEC</p>
            <h3>Read</h3>
            <p>The normative core documents for TIM, Notary, Kernel, Settlers, and Policy Packs.</p>
            <div class="path-links">
              <a class="path-link" href="https://github.com/arky-foundation/arky.foundation/blob/master/specs/core/README.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open core specs</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="path-card reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 90ms">
            <p class="claim">2 / VERIFY</p>
            <h3>Validate</h3>
            <p>Recompute every artifact locally and replay the published vectors against the Rust reference stack.</p>
            <div class="terminal">
              <div class="terminal-head">
                <span>core-rs conformance</span>
                <button class="copy-command" type="button" data-copy="cargo test -p arky-core">copy</button>
              </div>
              <pre><code>cargo test -p arky-core</code></pre>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="path-card reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 180ms">
            <p class="claim">3 / IMPLEMENT</p>
            <h3>Build</h3>
            <p>Use the TypeScript and Rust reference packages as executable anchors for conformant behavior.</p>
            <div class="path-links">
              <a class="path-link" href="https://github.com/arky-foundation/arky.foundation/blob/master/packages/core/README.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TypeScript</a>
              <a class="path-link" href="https://github.com/arky-foundation/arky.foundation/blob/master/packages/core-rs/README.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Rust</a>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="band section" aria-labelledby="domains-title">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="section-grid">
          <div class="section-head reveal">
            <p class="section-label">Adopters</p>
            <h2 id="domains-title">One receipt language across industries.</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="lead reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 100ms">Rail-agnostic and policy-aware &mdash; the same surface, adopted wherever an action needs proof.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="domain-list">
          <article class="domain reveal">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M10 18h28M10 30h28M18 10v28M30 10v28" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"></path>
              <rect x="14" y="14" width="20" height="20" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"></rect>
            </svg>
            <h3>AI and agents</h3>
            <p>Action records with cited evidence and declared policy.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="domain reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 80ms">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M10 18h28v18H10zM14 18v-4h20v4M16 27h16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"></path>
            </svg>
            <h3>Finance</h3>
            <p>Receipts that connect decisions to rails and outcomes.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="domain reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 160ms">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M12 18h10v10H12zM26 10h10v10H26zM26 28h10v10H26zM22 23h4M31 20v8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"></path>
            </svg>
            <h3>Blockchain</h3>
            <p>Neutral verification without capture by any one chain.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="domain reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 240ms">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M24 8l6 12 12 6-12 4-6 10-6-10-12-4 12-6zM24 8v32" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
            </svg>
            <h3>Space and robotics</h3>
            <p>Trust under latency, offline verification, and delayed settlement.</p>
          </article>
        </div>

        <div class="closing reveal">
          <p class="closing-text">Ready to adopt? Read the spec, replay the vectors, and ship conformance against two independent reference stacks.</p>
